{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"28":"Foods (Kitab Al-At'imah)"},"section_detail":{"28":{"hadithnumber_first":3736,"hadithnumber_last":3854,"arabicnumber_first":3736,"arabicnumber_last":3854}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3841,"arabicnumber":3841,"text":"Rapporté par Maymouna رضي الله عنها : Une souris est tombée dans du beurre clarifié. On en a informé le Prophète ﷺ. Il a dit : « Retirez ce qui est autour et mangez. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (5538)"}],"reference":{"book":28,"hadith":106}}]}